<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Jade 第二次課程｜Abby Eat Life</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+TC:wght@400;500;700&family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,500;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --sage: #8B9E7E;
  --terra: #C17F59;
  --cream: #FDFBF7;
  --bark: #3D3229;
  --sage-light: #e8ede5;
  --terra-light: #f5e6db;
  --blue: #5B82A6;
  --blue-light: #dce8f2;
  --bg: #FDFBF7;
  --bg-2: #f3f0ea;
  --border: rgba(61,50,41,0.11);
  --border-md: rgba(61,50,41,0.22);
  --text: #2a2218;
  --text-2: #6b5e52;
  --text-3: #a0948a;
  --r-md: 8px;
  --r-lg: 14px;
}
*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0;}
body{font-family:'Noto Sans TC',sans-serif;background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);font-size:15px;line-height:1.7;min-height:100vh;}

/* HEADER */
.hdr{background:var(--bark);color:var(--cream);padding:1.25rem 2rem;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;position:sticky;top:0;z-index:100;}
.hdr-dot{width:34px;height:34px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--sage);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#fff;flex-shrink:0;}
.hdr h1{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:18px;font-weight:500;}
.hdr .sub{font-size:12px;opacity:0.55;margin-top:1px;}
.hdr-badge{margin-left:auto;background:rgba(139,158,126,0.3);border:0.5px solid rgba(139,158,126,0.5);color:var(--sage-light);font-size:11px;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:12px;white-space:nowrap;}

/* LAYOUT */
.layout{display:flex;min-height:calc(100vh - 64px);}
.sidebar{width:196px;flex-shrink:0;background:#fff;border-right:0.5px solid var(--border);padding:1rem 0;position:sticky;top:64px;height:calc(100vh - 64px);overflow-y:auto;}
.sg-label{font-size:10px;color:var(--text-3);padding:0.6rem 1.1rem 0.2rem;letter-spacing:0.07em;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;}
.sb-btn{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;width:100%;padding:7px 1.1rem;background:none;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-family:'Noto Sans TC',sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:var(--text-2);text-align:left;transition:all 0.13s;}
.sb-btn:hover{background:var(--bg-2);color:var(--text);}
.sb-btn.active{background:var(--sage-light);color:var(--sage);font-weight:500;}
.sb-btn.active .bdg-a{background:var(--sage);color:#fff;}
.sb-btn.active .bdg-b{background:var(--terra);color:#fff;}
.sb-btn.active .bdg-c{background:var(--blue);color:#fff;}
.bdg{width:19px;height:19px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0;}
.bdg-a{background:var(--sage-light);color:var(--sage);}
.bdg-b{background:var(--terra-light);color:var(--terra);}
.bdg-c{background:var(--blue-light);color:var(--blue);}

.main{flex:1;padding:1.75rem 2rem;max-width:800px;}
.sec{display:none;}
.sec.on{display:block;}

/* SECTION HEADER */
.sec-hdr{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;margin-bottom:1.4rem;padding-bottom:1rem;border-bottom:0.5px solid var(--border);}
.sec-bdg{width:30px;height:30px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0;}
.sec-title{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:17px;font-weight:500;}

/* CARDS */
.card{background:#fff;border:0.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--r-lg);padding:1.1rem 1.3rem;margin-bottom:1rem;}
.card-lbl{font-size:11px;color:var(--text-3);margin-bottom:10px;letter-spacing:0.04em;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;}

.g4{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(130px,1fr));gap:10px;margin-bottom:1rem;}
.g2{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(200px,1fr));gap:10px;margin-bottom:1rem;}
.g3{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(150px,1fr));gap:10px;margin-bottom:1rem;}

.mc{background:var(--bg-2);border-radius:var(--r-md);padding:0.85rem 1rem;}
.mc-lbl{font-size:11px;color:var(--text-2);margin-bottom:3px;}
.mc-val{font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:var(--text);}
.mc-note{font-size:11px;color:var(--text-3);margin-top:2px;}

.chart-wrap{position:relative;width:100%;height:200px;margin:0.75rem 0;}

/* TAGS */
.tag{display:inline-block;font-size:11px;padding:3px 9px;border-radius:10px;margin:2px;}
.tok{background:var(--sage-light);color:#4a6b3e;}
.twarn{background:#fef3e2;color:#a06010;}
.talert{background:#fdecea;color:#a03030;}
.tblue{background:var(--blue-light);color:var(--blue);}

/* INFO ROWS */
.ir{display:flex;gap:10px;align-items:flex-start;padding:9px 0;border-bottom:0.5px solid var(--border);font-size:14px;}
.ir:last-child{border-bottom:none;}
.ir-ico{color:var(--text-3);flex-shrink:0;padding-top:2px;font-size:15px;width:20px;text-align:center;}
.ir-txt{color:var(--text);line-height:1.65;}
.ir-txt strong{font-weight:600;}

/* PROGRESS */
.pr{margin-bottom:0.9rem;}
.pr-lbl{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-size:13px;margin-bottom:4px;}
.pr-lbl span:first-child{color:var(--text-2);}
.pr-lbl span:last-child{color:var(--text);font-weight:600;}
.pr-bg{height:7px;background:var(--bg-2);border-radius:4px;overflow:hidden;}
.pr-fill{height:100%;border-radius:4px;transition:width 0.7s ease;}
.pr-note{font-size:11px;color:var(--text-3);margin-top:3px;}

/* BOXES */
.tip{background:var(--sage-light);border-left:3px solid var(--sage);border-radius:0 var(--r-md) var(--r-md) 0;padding:10px 14px;font-size:13px;color:var(--text);line-height:1.65;margin-top:0.75rem;}
.warn{background:var(--terra-light);border-left:3px solid var(--terra);border-radius:0 var(--r-md) var(--r-md) 0;padding:10px 14px;font-size:13px;color:var(--text);line-height:1.65;margin-top:0.75rem;}
.blue-box{background:var(--blue-light);border-left:3px solid var(--blue);border-radius:0 var(--r-md) var(--r-md) 0;padding:10px 14px;font-size:13px;color:var(--text);line-height:1.65;margin-top:0.75rem;}

/* GOAL ROWS */
.gr{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:12px;padding:9px 0;border-bottom:0.5px solid var(--border);font-size:14px;}
.gr:last-child{border-bottom:none;}
.gr-num{width:24px;height:24px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px;}
.gr-a{background:var(--sage-light);color:var(--sage);}
.gr-b{background:var(--terra-light);color:var(--terra);}
.gr-c{background:var(--blue-light);color:var(--blue);}
.gr-txt{color:var(--text);line-height:1.55;}
.gr-sub{color:var(--text-2);font-size:12px;margin-top:2px;}

/* TABLE */
.tbl{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:13px;}
.tbl th{background:var(--bg-2);font-weight:600;padding:7px 11px;text-align:left;color:var(--text-2);font-size:11px;border-bottom:0.5px solid var(--border);letter-spacing:0.02em;}
.tbl td{padding:8px 11px;border-bottom:0.5px solid var(--border);color:var(--text);vertical-align:top;}
.tbl tr:last-child td{border-bottom:none;}
.hl-g{color:#2e7d32;font-weight:600;}
.hl-r{color:#c0392b;font-weight:600;}
.hl-o{color:#a06010;font-weight:600;}

/* WEEK COMPARISON */
.wk-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr;gap:1px;background:var(--border);border-radius:var(--r-md);overflow:hidden;margin-top:10px;}
.wk-col{background:#fff;padding:10px 12px;}
.wk-col:first-child{background:var(--bg-2);}
.wk-head{font-size:11px;color:var(--text-3);margin-bottom:6px;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.04em;}
.wk-val{font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:var(--text);}
.wk-sub{font-size:11px;color:var(--text-2);margin-top:2px;}
.wk-delta{font-size:13px;font-weight:700;margin-top:4px;}
.delta-g{color:#2e7d32;}
.delta-r{color:#c0392b;}

/* SCENARIO CARD */
.sc-card{border:0.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--r-lg);overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:0.75rem;}
.sc-head{padding:10px 14px;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;}
.sc-head-a{background:var(--sage-light);color:#3d5c35;}
.sc-head-b{background:var(--terra-light);color:#7a4a2a;}
.sc-head-c{background:var(--blue-light);color:#2d5278;}
.sc-body{padding:10px 14px;font-size:13px;color:var(--text);line-height:1.65;background:#fff;}

/* INSULIN VISUAL */
.ins-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0;margin:8px 0;}
.ins-label{font-size:12px;color:var(--text-2);width:110px;flex-shrink:0;}
.ins-bar-wrap{flex:1;height:20px;background:var(--bg-2);border-radius:4px;overflow:hidden;position:relative;}
.ins-fill{height:100%;border-radius:4px;display:flex;align-items:center;padding-left:8px;font-size:10px;color:#fff;font-weight:600;}
.ins-note{font-size:11px;color:var(--text-3);width:80px;text-align:right;flex-shrink:0;padding-left:8px;}

/* PROTEIN TRACKER */
.pt-wrap{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin:10px 0;}
.pt-label{font-size:13px;color:var(--text-2);width:80px;flex-shrink:0;}
.pt-bar-wrap{flex:1;height:12px;background:var(--bg-2);border-radius:6px;overflow:hidden;}
.pt-fill{height:100%;border-radius:6px;transition:width 0.6s ease;}
.pt-val{font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text);width:60px;text-align:right;flex-shrink:0;}

@media(max-width:640px){
  .layout{flex-direction:column;}
  .sidebar{width:100%;height:auto;position:static;display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;padding:0.5rem;gap:3px;}
  .sg-label{display:none;}
  .sb-btn{border-radius:16px;padding:5px 10px;width:auto;}
  .sb-btn.active{background:var(--sage);color:#fff;}
  .main{padding:1rem;}
  .wk-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="hdr">
  <div class="hdr-dot">J</div>
  <div>
    <h1>Jade 第二次課程</h1>
    <div class="sub">2026.06.08 ｜ Abby Eat Life 營養 Coaching</div>
  </div>

</div>

<div class="layout">
  <nav class="sidebar">
    <div class="sg-label">本週回顧</div>
    <button class="sb-btn active" onclick="show('a1',this)"><span class="bdg bdg-a">A1</span>體重進度</button>
    <button class="sb-btn" onclick="show('a2',this)"><span class="bdg bdg-a">A2</span>飲食分析</button>
    <button class="sb-btn" onclick="show('a3',this)"><span class="bdg bdg-a">A3</span>執行亮點</button>
    <div class="sg-label" style="margin-top:0.5rem;">新觀念</div>
    <button class="sb-btn" onclick="show('b1',this)"><span class="bdg bdg-b">B1</span>代謝適應</button>
    <button class="sb-btn" onclick="show('b2',this)"><span class="bdg bdg-b">B2</span>蛋白質提升</button>
    <button class="sb-btn" onclick="show('b3',this)"><span class="bdg bdg-b">B3</span>聚餐策略</button>
    <div class="sg-label" style="margin-top:0.5rem;">進階概念</div>
    <button class="sb-btn" onclick="show('c1',this)"><span class="bdg bdg-c">C1</span>血糖波動</button>
    <button class="sb-btn" onclick="show('c2',this)"><span class="bdg bdg-c">C2</span>下階段目標</button>
  </nav>

  <main class="main">

    <!-- A1 體重進度 -->
    <div class="sec on" id="sec-a1">
      <div class="sec-hdr">
        <div class="sec-bdg bdg-a">A1</div>
        <div class="sec-title">體重進度回顧</div>
      </div>

      <div class="wk-grid">
        <div class="wk-col">
          <div class="wk-head">基準（第一週）</div>
          <div class="wk-val">74.1 kg</div>
          <div class="wk-sub">5/19–5/24 週均</div>
        </div>
        <div class="wk-col">
          <div class="wk-head">第二週</div>
          <div class="wk-val">72.6 kg</div>
          <div class="wk-sub">5/26–6/1 週均</div>
          <div class="wk-delta delta-g">↓ 1.5 kg</div>
        </div>
        <div class="wk-col">
          <div class="wk-head">第三週</div>
          <div class="wk-val">72.0 kg</div>
          <div class="wk-sub">6/2–6/7 週均</div>
          <div class="wk-delta delta-g">↓ 0.6 kg</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card" style="margin-top:1rem;">
        <div class="card-lbl">兩週體重曲線</div>
        <div class="chart-wrap">
          <canvas id="weightChart" role="img" aria-label="Jade體重從74公斤下降至71.9公斤的折線圖"></canvas>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="g3">
        <div class="mc">
          <div class="mc-lbl">兩週總降幅</div>
          <div class="mc-val" style="color:var(--sage);">↓ 2.1 kg</div>
          <div class="mc-note">目標 1 kg，超標完成 ✓</div>
        </div>
        <div class="mc">
          <div class="mc-lbl">目前最低紀錄</div>
          <div class="mc-val">71.9 kg</div>
          <div class="mc-note">6/7（日）</div>
        </div>
        <div class="mc">
          <div class="mc-lbl">距離目標</div>
          <div class="mc-val">7.0 kg</div>
          <div class="mc-note">目標 65 kg</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-lbl">這次降得快，原因是什麼？</div>
        <div class="ir">
          <div class="ir-ico">💧</div>
          <div class="ir-txt"><strong>水腫消退（約佔一半）</strong>：飲食改善後鈉攝取大降，組織間積水開始排出，這部分不是脂肪</div>
        </div>
        <div class="ir">
          <div class="ir-ico">⚡</div>
          <div class="ir-txt"><strong>肝醣消耗</strong>：熱量稍低於維持量，肝醣儲存下降，每克肝醣帶走約 3g 水，體重視覺上降得快</div>
        </div>
        <div class="ir">
          <div class="ir-ico">🔥</div>
          <div class="ir-txt"><strong>真正的脂肪燃燒</strong>：持續的熱量赤字在這兩週也有實質的脂肪消耗，估計約 0.5–0.8 kg</div>
        </div>
        <div class="warn">接下來體重會趨緩——這是正常的，不是出問題。水腫退完、肝醣穩定後，進入穩定脂肪燃燒期，每週 0.5 kg 才是持續的速度。</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- A2 飲食分析 -->
    <div class="sec" id="sec-a2">
      <div class="sec-hdr">
        <div class="sec-bdg bdg-a">A2</div>
        <div class="sec-title">飲食數據分析（12天均值）</div>
      </div>

      <div class="g4">
        <div class="mc">
          <div class="mc-lbl">估算日均熱量</div>
          <div class="mc-val" style="color:var(--terra);">1,325</div>
          <div class="mc-note">kcal（目標 1,500）</div>
        </div>
        <div class="mc">
          <div class="mc-lbl">蛋白質均值</div>
          <div class="mc-val" style="color:var(--terra);">91 g</div>
          <div class="mc-note">目標 120 g，差 29 g</div>
        </div>
        <div class="mc">
          <div class="mc-lbl">碳水均值</div>
          <div class="mc-val" style="color:var(--sage);">122 g</div>
          <div class="mc-note">目標 120–150 g ✓</div>
        </div>
        <div class="mc">
          <div class="mc-lbl">脂肪均值</div>
          <div class="mc-val" style="color:var(--sage);">47 g</div>
          <div class="mc-note">目標約 50 g ✓</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-lbl">三大營養素達成率</div>
        <div style="margin-top:10px;">
          <div class="pr">
            <div class="pr-lbl"><span>熱量</span><span>1,325 / 1,500 kcal</span></div>
            <div class="pr-bg"><div class="pr-fill" style="width:88%;background:var(--terra);"></div></div>
            <div class="pr-note">⚠️ 偏低 175 kcal，需往上吃一點</div>
          </div>
          <div class="pr">
            <div class="pr-lbl"><span>蛋白質</span><span>91 / 120 g</span></div>
            <div class="pr-bg"><div class="pr-fill" style="width:76%;background:var(--terra);"></div></div>
            <div class="pr-note">⚠️ 仍差約 29 g，是目前最主要的缺口</div>
          </div>
          <div class="pr">
            <div class="pr-lbl"><span>碳水化合物</span><span>122 / 130 g</span></div>
            <div class="pr-bg"><div class="pr-fill" style="width:94%;background:var(--sage);"></div></div>
            <div class="pr-note">✅ 達標，品質也有提升</div>
          </div>
          <div class="pr">
            <div class="pr-lbl"><span>脂肪</span><span>47 / 50 g</span></div>
            <div class="pr-bg"><div class="pr-fill" style="width:94%;background:var(--sage);"></div></div>
            <div class="pr-note">✅ 接近目標</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-lbl">每日熱量分佈（12天）</div>
        <div class="chart-wrap">
          <canvas id="kcalChart" role="img" aria-label="12天每日熱量分布長條圖"></canvas>
        </div>
        <div class="warn">5/30（僅銀耳蓮子湯＋聚餐）和 6/1、6/5 熱量明顯偏低，這幾天蛋白質也特別不足，是最需要補強的情境。</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- A3 執行亮點 -->
    <div class="sec" id="sec-a3">
      <div class="sec-hdr">
        <div class="sec-bdg bdg-a">A3</div>
        <div class="sec-title">執行亮點 ＋ 觀察到的模式</div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-lbl">做得非常好的地方 👏</div>
        <div class="ir">
          <div class="ir-ico" style="color:var(--sage);">✓</div>
          <div class="ir-txt"><strong>烹調方式大幅改善</strong>：昆布鍋、烤、燙、蒸為主，炸物幾乎消失</div>
        </div>
        <div class="ir">
          <div class="ir-ico" style="color:var(--sage);">✓</div>
          <div class="ir-txt"><strong>蔬菜量和種類明顯增加</strong>：高麗菜、空心菜、花椰菜、蒟蒻絲、生菜都出現了</div>
        </div>
        <div class="ir">
          <div class="ir-ico" style="color:var(--sage);">✓</div>
          <div class="ir-txt"><strong>主動補蛋白質</strong>：優格、高蛋白粉加入日常，顯示有在執行</div>
        </div>
        <div class="ir">
          <div class="ir-ico" style="color:var(--sage);">✓</div>
          <div class="ir-txt"><strong>Omega-3 有進來</strong>：6/1 大量鮭魚、蝦仁，6/4 生魚片，方向完全正確</div>
        </div>
        <div class="ir">
          <div class="ir-ico" style="color:var(--sage);">✓</div>
          <div class="ir-txt"><strong>活動量提升</strong>：多次達到萬步，三次騎腳踏車，非常穩定</div>
        </div>
        <div class="ir">
          <div class="ir-ico" style="color:var(--sage);">✓</div>
          <div class="ir-txt"><strong>紀錄很細很完整</strong>：連克數都有記，資料品質很高</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-lbl">需要優化的模式</div>
        <div class="ir">
          <div class="ir-ico">⚠️</div>
          <div class="ir-txt"><strong>部分日子只有兩餐</strong>：6/2、6/5 進食間隔過長，容易讓蛋白質合成效率下降</div>
        </div>
        <div class="ir">
          <div class="ir-ico">⚠️</div>
